Reports/Analytics expected from PMT
	Gross Profit from project
		Timesheet will be input for analytics
		Resource Expenses for project will be salary per day plus billable bonus for the day
		8 hours of work done for project will be considered as a day or vice versa
		Resource bill will be added to registered expenses alongwith some project level expenses
		Revenue of project (i.e. invoices paid) will be recorded seperately in admin panel
